<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 22:06:03 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>加沙战争必须立即停止</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-19/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-war-in-gaza-must-stop-immediately/0000018b-43ec-d614-abcf-ebff3ecd0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 21:25:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-19/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-war-in-gaza-must-stop-immediately/0000018b-43ec-d614-abcf-ebff3ecd0000</guid></item><item><title>西方左派不是虚伪，而是疯狂</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-19/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-western-left-isnt-hypocritical-its-deranged/0000018b-4411-d242-abef-56379cbb0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 21:23:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-19/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-western-left-isnt-hypocritical-its-deranged/0000018b-4411-d242-abef-56379cbb0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登展示了美国对以色列及其安全的承诺</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-10-18/ty-article-opinion/biden-demonstrated-americas-commitment-to-israel-and-its-security/0000018b-4449-df22-a5eb-4d79e7ce0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 20:57:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-10-18/ty-article-opinion/biden-demonstrated-americas-commitment-to-israel-and-its-security/0000018b-4449-df22-a5eb-4d79e7ce0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登授予以色列的巨大胡萝卜旁边悬着一根大棒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/a-big-stick-hovers-beside-the-huge-carrots-being-granted-to-israel-by-biden/0000018b-4466-de3d-a58f-cc6f6b370000</link><description>以色列执政党的部长和立法者敦促他管好自己的事，不要干涉我们的生活并尊重我们的民主，拜登以一种不亚于历史性的方式团结在我们一边</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 20:56:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/a-big-stick-hovers-beside-the-huge-carrots-being-granted-to-israel-by-biden/0000018b-4466-de3d-a58f-cc6f6b370000</guid></item><item><title>以色列为加沙边境社区撤离人员提供创伤支持的计划依赖于志愿者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/israels-trauma-support-to-evacuees-of-gaza-border-communities-relies-on-volunteers/0000018b-4442-d614-abcf-ec73a55a0000</link><description>精神病医院的管理人员紧急呼吁志愿者，因为他们有限的人员无法为撤离者提供情绪急救。专家和组织在过去十年中多次警告说，公共心理健康系统正在被摧毁</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 20:52:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/israels-trauma-support-to-evacuees-of-gaza-border-communities-relies-on-volunteers/0000018b-4442-d614-abcf-ec73a55a0000</guid></item><item><title>共和党在参议院听证会上猛烈抨击拜登下一任美国驻以色列大使候选人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/gop-hammers-bidens-candidate-for-next-u-s-ambassador-to-israel-in-senate-hearing/0000018b-43e1-de3d-a58f-cbe9aad40000</link><description>共和党的攻击发生在拜登政府提名卢的关键考虑因素之一之际，即在国会在推动提名人前进方面遇到前所未有的困难的情况下，他通过确认程序的潜在能力</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 18:25:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/gop-hammers-bidens-candidate-for-next-u-s-ambassador-to-israel-in-senate-hearing/0000018b-43e1-de3d-a58f-cbe9aad40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人需要的不仅仅是“摧毁哈马斯”的模糊要求</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article-opinion/israelis-need-more-than-a-vague-demand-to-destroy-hamas/0000018b-43dc-df22-a5eb-4bfdecc10000</link><description>在第二次世界大战最黑暗的时期，罗斯福和丘吉尔规划了战后的未来。现在是政府提出以色列愿景的时候了，为了这个愿景，数百万士兵和平民被要求冒着生命危险，甚至牺牲生命</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 18:09:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article-opinion/israelis-need-more-than-a-vague-demand-to-destroy-hamas/0000018b-43dc-df22-a5eb-4bfdecc10000</guid></item><item><title>对于哈马斯来说，加沙医院悲剧是一场叙事性的胜利</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-10-18/ty-article/.highlight/for-hamas-the-gaza-hospital-tragedy-is-a-narrative-victory/0000018b-43c2-d242-abef-53e6960a0000</link><description>越来越多的证据更加有力地证明了以色列关于加沙城阿赫利圣公会医院悲剧如何发生的说法，但损害已经造成。与此同时，加沙人将埋葬他们的死者，他们已成为国际影响力游戏中的棋子</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 17:47:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-10-18/ty-article/.highlight/for-hamas-the-gaza-hospital-tragedy-is-a-narrative-victory/0000018b-43c2-d242-abef-53e6960a0000</guid></item><item><title>新发现改变了哈薛国王攻击圣经迦特的故事</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-10-18/ty-article-magazine/new-discovery-changes-story-of-king-hazaels-attack-on-biblical-gath/0000018b-43ab-de3d-a58f-cbeb50e70000</link><description>迦特的非利士人被认为是黎凡特地区使用美索不达米亚风格的烧砖建筑的异类。但在 Tell es-Safi 烧制砖块的并不是窑炉</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 17:35:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-10-18/ty-article-magazine/new-discovery-changes-story-of-king-hazaels-attack-on-biblical-gath/0000018b-43ab-de3d-a58f-cbeb50e70000</guid></item><item><title>拜登在对以色列进行史无前例的战时访问期间回顾了大屠杀和9月11日</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/biden-evokes-holocaust-and-september-11-during-unprecedented-wartime-visit-to-israel/0000018b-4352-d614-abcf-eb7346480000</link><description>美国总统宣称“10 月 7 日是自大屠杀以来对犹太人来说最致命的一天”，并发誓“不会再袖手旁观，什么也不做，今天不会，明天不会，永远不会”</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 17:17:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/biden-evokes-holocaust-and-september-11-during-unprecedented-wartime-visit-to-israel/0000018b-4352-d614-abcf-eb7346480000</guid></item><item><title>数万人签署请愿书，要求驱逐被视为亲哈马斯的美国教授</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/tens-of-thousands-sign-petitions-demanding-ousters-of-u-s-professors-seen-as-pro-hamas/0000018b-438b-df22-a5eb-4bfbe9360000</link><description>康奈尔大学、哥伦比亚大学和耶鲁大学的教职人员要求解雇那些将哈马斯对以色列南部的袭击形容为令人振奋和震惊的研究员。耶鲁大学的一位教授说：“巴勒斯坦人完全有权通过武装斗争进行抵抗”</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 17:07:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/tens-of-thousands-sign-petitions-demanding-ousters-of-u-s-professors-seen-as-pro-hamas/0000018b-438b-df22-a5eb-4bfbe9360000</guid></item><item><title>“如果她落入哈马斯手中，我们不知道她将如何在克罗恩病中生存”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/if-shes-in-the-hands-of-hamas-we-dont-know-how-shell-survive-with-crohns/0000018b-4328-de3d-a58f-cb693a160000</link><description>被哈马斯扣为人质的以色列家庭：一个特殊项目 ■ Tamar Gutman 很高兴。在与一种使人衰弱的疾病抗争了几年后，她精神焕发，很高兴能够参加超新星音乐节。她的家人谈论她以及收集信息的尝试</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 15:55:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/if-shes-in-the-hands-of-hamas-we-dont-know-how-shell-survive-with-crohns/0000018b-4328-de3d-a58f-cb693a160000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府未批准解决巴勒斯坦囚犯过度拥挤问题的临时计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/israels-knesset-approves-temporal-prison-overcrowding-for-palestinian-prisoners/0000018b-4333-d242-abef-533795bc0000</link><description>十六名以色列立法者投票赞成这项临时规定，该规定将持续三个月，并使该国的监狱即使在满负荷的情况下也能接纳新囚犯</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 15:42:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/israels-knesset-approves-temporal-prison-overcrowding-for-palestinian-prisoners/0000018b-4333-d242-abef-533795bc0000</guid></item><item><title>17名记者确认在以色列、加沙和黎巴嫩死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/17-journalists-confirmed-dead-in-israel-gaza-and-lebanon/0000018b-4311-d614-abcf-eb7349530000</link><description>保护记者委员会周三表示，自 10 月 7 日哈马斯在以色列南部发动致命袭击以来，已有 3 名以色列记者、1 名黎巴嫩记者和 13 名巴勒斯坦记者死亡。有关其他记者被杀、失踪、拘留、受伤或威胁的报道正在接受调查</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 15:25:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/17-journalists-confirmed-dead-in-israel-gaza-and-lebanon/0000018b-4311-d614-abcf-eb7349530000</guid></item><item><title>观看：加沙医院火箭爆炸背后的视频及其内容</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-presents-data-showing-attack-on-gaza-hospital-caused-by-failed-islamic-jihad-rocket/0000018b-42d6-d259-a3bb-cef74fd70000</link><description>以色列军队展示了半岛电视台的一段视频，以证明伊斯兰圣战组织对加沙医院爆炸负有责任</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 15:04:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-presents-data-showing-attack-on-gaza-hospital-caused-by-failed-islamic-jihad-rocket/0000018b-42d6-d259-a3bb-cef74fd70000</guid></item><item><title>由于以色列断水断电，加沙人面临脱水和疾病的风险</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/with-no-water-or-electricity-from-israel-gazans-risk-dehydration-and-disease/0000018b-42ff-d614-abcf-eaff15d80000</link><description>即使在“平时”，加沙90%的自来水也无法饮用，战争期间情况变得更糟</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 14:15:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/with-no-water-or-electricity-from-israel-gazans-risk-dehydration-and-disease/0000018b-42ff-d614-abcf-eaff15d80000</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯官方媒体称以色列在加沙的报复行动是“法西斯主义”，要求对撤离令实施制裁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/russian-media-calls-israeli-retaliation-in-gaza-fascism-demands-sanctions/0000018b-423e-d242-abef-523e7d060000</link><description>俄罗斯电视节目主持人将以色列与乌克兰进行比较，称加沙的行动是“令人震惊的残忍行为”；说不应该对以色列人“有一丝怜悯或同情”</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 11:16:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/russian-media-calls-israeli-retaliation-in-gaza-fascism-demands-sanctions/0000018b-423e-d242-abef-523e7d060000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯的恐怖视频：“我们在争取公众意识的斗争中落后了光年”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/we-are-light-years-behind-hamas-in-the-battle-for-public-consciousness/0000018b-3d0f-d07d-a99b-fdcf93100000</link><description>以色列传统媒体选择过滤哈马斯传播的可怕屠杀画面，但社交媒体却充斥着这样的画面。社交媒体将如何影响以色列的军事行动？图片如何改变了越南和黎巴嫩的战争进程？</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 10:59:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/we-are-light-years-behind-hamas-in-the-battle-for-public-consciousness/0000018b-3d0f-d07d-a99b-fdcf93100000</guid></item><item><title>创伤可以让以色列公众睁开眼睛。是时候组建和平内阁了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article-opinion/.premium/trauma-can-open-the-israeli-publics-eyes-time-for-a-peace-cabinet/0000018b-4238-d242-abef-523e3eea0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 10:24:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article-opinion/.premium/trauma-can-open-the-israeli-publics-eyes-time-for-a-peace-cabinet/0000018b-4238-d242-abef-523e3eea0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙医院爆炸后，伊斯坦布尔警方阻止袭击以色列领事馆</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/istanbul-police-averts-attempt-to-storm-israeli-consulate-after-gaza-hospital-explosion/0000018b-4231-d242-abef-523752720000</link><description>伊斯坦布尔省长办公室称，周三早些时候，一群人用石头、棍棒和烟花袭击领事馆大楼，造成 60 多人受伤，其中大部分是警察</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 10:16:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/istanbul-police-averts-attempt-to-storm-israeli-consulate-after-gaza-hospital-explosion/0000018b-4231-d242-abef-523752720000</guid></item></channel></rss>